## Enforcement

**This rule is MANDATORY and CRITICAL. Violations are not acceptable.**

**Checklist - After EVERY change, verify:**
- [ ] Did I make changes? → If YES, proceed to commit
- [ ] Did I run `git add .`? → If NO, do it now
- [ ] Did I run `git commit -m "message"`? → If NO, do it now
- [ ] Did I run `git push`? → If NO, do it now
- [ ] Are there uncommitted changes? → If YES, commit them NOW

**If you find yourself with uncommitted changes, STOP what you're doing and commit them immediately.**

